      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<style type=\"text/css\">.fixed-table {\n    width: 100% !important;\n    table-layout: fixed !important;\n  }\n  .fixed-table td {\n    white-space: normal !important;\n    word-break: break-word !important;\n    overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\n    vertical-align: top;\n  }\n  .w-20 { width: 20% !important; }\n  .w-30 { width: 30% !important; }\n  .w-40 { width: 40% !important; }\n  .w-50 { width: 50% !important; }\n  .w-60 { width: 60% !important; }\n  .w-70 { width: 70% !important; }\n</style>\n<p>Liferay DXP 2025.Q3 Quarterly Release is only supported under the following certified configurations:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7DTB41PNF6P6EAXARM\"><a href=\"#application-server\" id=\"application-server\">Application Server</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e6ea7148758e81c708bd6d05955ee99bf\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Apache Tomcat 10.1</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e7c4285e2b1464ee487ec073a5dbc844d\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JBoss EAP 8.0</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e7fe8a956de1e3ff1a06dc9f19ebb25cb\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Wildfly 30</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<p>For more information on configurations and limitations with Application Servers that are compatible with Liferay DXP, please refer to the <a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/installation-and-upgrades/installing-liferay\">Liferay User Guide</a>&nbsp;and our <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360015739932-Installation#Application-Servers\" rel=\"undefined\" target=\"_self\">Support Policy</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7GF6D1WG1PKEACM2DD\"><a href=\"#database\" id=\"database\">Database</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e4ac9c6932969825b7546cee2410c94f1\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Amazon Aurora</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eaad76a23d6f79570d9fde6b717fbe17a\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">DB2 11.1</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ea3b4fbc6f02f047045ff100eab07304e\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">DB2 11.5</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eaae3644684080653ca5b173a863930d6\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MariaDB 10.2</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ee51fc756a6db507b2b01e74d4e75b6d7\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MariaDB 10.4</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ed3f1000e87a194ddc7d66a55eeaba613\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MariaDB 10.6</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e4838838d72707139696d10939711dc5f\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MySQL 5.7</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eb590de0bc184388c0f8f2bc43720a0ce\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MySQL 8.0</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e0acc2e64f50ebc31af2cbec38c56b2bd\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MySQL 8.4</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e7824de36688ab16ae7c7342e4bd83862\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle 19c</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5195bebb948e91fa961845ff59b1bab1\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 12.x</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ef29badcd812b2f7abd5565b478551605\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 13.x</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e115397a4f1a028aa12f7d1aefbd9765f\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 14.x</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e21e85e98acdc40c2837a2dbb0a7582cc\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 15.x</span><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e01707bf60502de82118c5ace45d2a3bf\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 16.x</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e6dc14587199a6853388d1c6edb312b47\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SQL Server 2017</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e2c50c43c183d797379e6006f4d58a9f7\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SQL Server 2019</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"ea170fc4860dac0fe9c0c9f5dd22aeb97\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SQL Server 2022</span><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<p>For more information on configurations and limitations with Databases compatible with Liferay DXP, please refer to the <a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/installation-and-upgrades/installing-liferay\">Liferay User Guide</a>&nbsp;and our <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360015739932-Installation#Databases\" rel=\"undefined\" target=\"_self\">Support Policy</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7H2PZPEMQ4W3YEM20V\"><a href=\"#operating-system\" id=\"operating-system\">Operating System</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e3c37cc68ac335d79f4979b904e5b3113\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Alpine Linux 3.13</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ef7418da969d93828ff538799eccf5fde\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Amazon Linux 2</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5722fbffed11c05dd337063f810a40e5\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Amazon Linux 2023</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"effbd914d996b9dfdaec5e59c060812fc\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CentOS 7</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ee84b0ec233f947ac71dd0204e2538e82\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CentOS 8</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e80d2c4860c2cf1a18f63bc2947d2e4fe\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Debian 10</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e92539cdd818488f7134e9a9e2ccc140b\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Debian 11</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e694de1aa2b96d23e93402e369ad064c1\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Debian 12</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e7f4e2f9fc101055a2e5c7223b666b39b\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Fedora Linux</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ea11de195282b6dfa9362242f2dcb7641\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">IBM AIX 7.2</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e692791e1ae8ba1b700ca23a636666822\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle Linux 7</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5a45844e1966fddaba5f338b01208d34\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle Linux 8</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e0d19dc849f5ef370d34066c8cc86714a\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle Linux 9</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eeef992aa7578c88d894d72bb7bb09277\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle Solaris 11</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e30db97ade7eb730a4b97a4e4d9b85887\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"edcb5b3bd6534a9810fbd9c7662dee226\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Red Hat Enterprise Linux 8</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e9ab9825b291ce4492f2ab155289d8736\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Red Hat Enterprise Linux 9</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5a3c4ea7cbbf9a5ebfb4a7f8fafa9527\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Rocky Linux 9</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e956f69c8d6bb389b0c998994cf63e711\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SUSE Enterprise Linux 12</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eb4185a54eb75f012e59a04584377709f\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SUSE Enterprise Linux 15</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e08e295834cf5097b2c36f13f764f02d2\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ubuntu LTS 18.04</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e10c9e66d4aa8132f4e6de466a0af3671\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ubuntu LTS 20.04</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e264f54ac7a12e46b5139ea0607e9389c\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ubuntu LTS 22.04</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ef05b7fc8643c38b4440860d812ddbe3b\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Server 2016</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e74e38a0ba916b76c8d8c8538dcd4e688\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Server 2019</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"ec41b4912ff0837c2a48e2f8e49a28c87\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Server 2022</span><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7HSCMX880DKXWY08R0\"><a href=\"#desktop-browser\" id=\"desktop-browser\">Desktop Browser</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e4fbf915955c509d79b330a26918be636\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Chrome (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e582c1c4b0096fbe3811b2eea30c46b19\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Edge (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e188b4e472f35f3533bd254e7743295c7\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Firefox ESR (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e947c2e70dcffb0953803ef7010b62c69\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Firefox (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e215884a5c4dd35d9ebb559dd95943198\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Safari (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<p>For more information on configurations and limitations with Desktop Browsers that are compatible with Liferay DXP, please refer to the <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360015739932#Browsers\" target=\"_self\">Support Policy</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7HQ0X3FK8W154RN4BB\"><a href=\"#mobile-browser\" id=\"mobile-browser\">Mobile Browser</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 50.8571%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 100%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e7fcb86b626b13ee4fabc699c3be4e9d5\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Chrome (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e3a799d4d7cb922a8a1be7426a4775b28\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Safari (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e98bca4c09673d47b1ab0050baf1cdc3f\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Edge (Latest)</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<p>Liferay will support access to information (e.g. reading content and navigation through pages), navigation menus, and basic responsiveness of modules for the latest versions of mobile browsers only. For more information on Liferay’s mobile support policy, please refer to the <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360018340411\" target=\"_self\">Help Center</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7JG1620AY12QAVVWNR\"><a href=\"#jdk\" id=\"jdk\">JDK</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"ef2d81789d3b3697448dfeb123f05a4bc\">Oracle JDK 17 <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/all-features/20004/25886767?r=25886767&amp;delta=20&amp;start=3#:~:text=Java%20JDK%2017%20runtime\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">DEPRECATED</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e1a73b7dc767dfbb10a44267e8a5239d6\">Oracle JDK 21</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eeb7df67da5d09502ae2df051f81486a3\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">All Java Technical Compatibility Kit (TCK) compliant builds of the respective Java major versions are certified</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7JBF1V1ZB0XVNH2G7Q\"><a href=\"#cloud-services\" id=\"cloud-services\">Cloud Services</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5bcd12fe6eb3aa9e403382bca6430bf5\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e54db4658e0052768f2e8b0038898a1a5\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Amazon Relational Database Service (RDS)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"ef17e588949051587a9b01ef172501685\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Amazon S3 (Object Storage)</span><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e78063964f3caf6a7996b6c7e08cd7f6f\">Azure Blob&nbsp;Storage</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e78063964f3caf6a7996b6c7e08cd7f6f\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Azure Files</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e37cbceb13f5241f6d9a4db6d5e6ccf79\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Azure SQL Databases</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e18a48befee34b09e4e2f19a7dedd305b\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Azure Virtual Machines</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5fd0678f7fb0332cb9146239a58ba13e\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Google Cloud Compute Engine (GCE)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ef8bd3e06f61606786775dc0680336cfc\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Google Cloud SQL</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e3e48ec02a4449c5aa5b730cab6160d89\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Google Cloud Object Storage</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e9fd1fd47553511bdce35f15447e23edf\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Red Hat OpenShift on IBM Cloud</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"eab1513ef2938657e3de666bc2917db38\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">IBM Cloud File Storage</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<p>Amazon EC2 and RDS are only supported with environments on the Liferay DXP Compatibility Matrix.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7JH8W7WVZRB3318TKA\"><a href=\"#search-engines\" id=\"search-engines\">Search Engines</a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 49.9263%;\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ee2ce2ac0909ae57b6ebd991f40cf2583\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Elasticsearch 8.8.x - 8.19.x</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ee3c20963d5736cbc25c6652505860275\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Elasticsearch 7.17.x </span><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/35072800462733\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">DEPRECATED</span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ef1ff6e01385505e12bede85e21182b5f\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenSearch 2.12.x - 2.19.x <mark>BETA</mark></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e8ee89fd9e695f3715b7a3aa7c48ad82e\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Solr 8.11.x </span><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\" style=\"background-color: hsl(0,0%,79%);\">MAINTENANCE MODE</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<p>The OpenSearch and Solr connectors are available on Liferay Marketplace. For the supported versions of Java, see the following pages: <a href=\"https://www.elastic.co/support/matrix#matrix_jvm\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Elasticsearch</a>, <a href=\"https://docs.opensearch.org/docs/2.16/install-and-configure/install-opensearch/index/#java-compatibility\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">OpenSearch</a>, <a href=\"https://solr.apache.org/guide/8_11/solr-system-requirements.html#java-requirements\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Solr</a>.</p>\n\n<p>For more information on configurations and limitations with Search Engines that are compatible with Liferay DXP, please refer to the <a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/using-search/installing-and-upgrading-a-search-engine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Documentation</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01K0WSHX2B76QKH0137K333Z74\"><a href=\"#integrated-technologies\" id=\"integrated-technologies\">Integrated Technologies</a></h2>\n\n<p>In addition to the certified configurations above, Liferay DXP can leverage some integrated or compatible technologies, specifically designed or tested with Liferay products. Other connectors may be present on the Liferay Marketplace. When integration is achieved through a standard or protocol, it may be possible to integrate technologies not listed on this matrix. However, Subscription Services is not required to assist with those integrations.</p>\n\n<p>Integrations which are compatible with Liferay products are implemented and tested for basic functionality of that technology. When a specific application is listed here it does not mean that all features of that application are compatible with Liferay products. Liferay will document, when known, if specific features of an application are not compatible with Liferay products.</p>\n\n<figure class=\"wysiwyg-table wysiwyg-table-align-left\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"3\" class=\"fixed-table\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"w-30\"><strong>Category</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"w-70\"><strong>Technologies</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; padding: 1px;\">Frontend Tooling</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5796e030f118d007e313e8ba4eace892\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">React 18</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e48cc2fcdba49f2b0a280837fc1b3c567\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CKeditor 4</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e8af78437a4509e63c31322d4bb702207\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CKeditor 5 (Beta)</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">Auto-Tagging</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ed248fa3eaadd55a56e7e088a435d5714\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">TensorFlow 3.0.35</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e453567dcc3e2788f79efa6e24f8d186a\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Google Cloud Vision</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ea64634c1fc9c704c1f655d86d004864b\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Google Cloud Natural Language</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e894b95c12461a02ff02e15623a71f4bd\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Microsoft AI Services (formerly Cognitive Services)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e956863918d71adaf4532c66ede10eb87\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenNLP</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">Document Conversion</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e3327e4ebd9b8f64c4437bbf3777cf7d9\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">LibreOffice 7.6.7</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ea0cc74ff1b35f1215f5ecb2a3fd72d1d\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenOffice4.1.11</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">External Repository Connectors</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e693b6de28c8f6d343f67bcd2b29a35df\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Sharepoint Online</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5043fae87cd564e10c6ca5175a4d73cd\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Alfresco 7.0 CE</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e2b00e5075a8b8ba2ebc425d4be71848d\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Nuxeo LTS 2021</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">Preview Generation</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e80bd31c4ddd4aa863ee089a15d07b0ec\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ghostscript 9.55</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ebf32d873d2bb3c61d1b177565d2b6b26\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">ImageMagick 7.1.1-43</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ec18ab7cce896b0824020a31439277fb2\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PDFBox 2.0.21</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e407381a6a94623db6681f542d3f5f7a4\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">HTML5</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e93a495bccc0664de7f0b32d066bdeb81\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Gifsicle 1.93</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP)</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ec765866169156f59648937242daa66ce\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay's LDAP integration relies on the <code>javax.naming.ldap</code> package, a Java API providing a standardized interface for accessing LDAP directories. This package enables Liferay to support a wide range of LDAPv3 functionalities, including extended operations and controls. All the software, services that are compliant with the same are supported.</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">SSO Standards &amp; Solutions</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e2864b6b6b42ee45211ec96d5dfd074ce\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenID Connect</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e545c87163173690c1dfe283af2dae83c\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SAML 2.0</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e5f50eb12d9d3460d7039d18112d913e9\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Facebook Connect</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ec57f2bda78db6029130f538a062f0ef5\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Kerberos</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e6ed324a392b7071c5bed39be14f81cf7\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Token-based SSO</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">Security Assertion Markup Language (SAML) Identity Providers (IdP)</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e3722a76d878f532239b22ef16658017c\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP is compliant with certain parts of the </span><a href=\"https://docs.oasis-open.org/security/saml/v2.0/saml-core-2.0-os.pdf\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Assertions and Protocols for the OASIS Security Assertion Markup Language (SAML) V2.0</span></a><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> and </span><a href=\"https://docs.oasis-open.org/security/saml/v2.0/saml-bindings-2.0-os.pdf\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">the Bindings for the OASIS Security Assertion Markup Language (SAML) V2.0 specs</span></a><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> marked by MUST and the related terms. All the software, services that are compliant with the same parts are supported.</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">OpenID Connect (OIDC) Providers</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e653470733ef12479810ed37bbeec54a0\">\n\t\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"5875\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP is compliant with mandatory features for Relying Parties detailed in the </span><a data-is-router-link=\"false\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" href=\"https://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-core-1_0.html\" title=\"https://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-core-1_0.html\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-underline\">Final: OpenID Connect Core 1.0 incorporating errata set 2</span></span></a><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">. All the software, services that are compliant with the same parts are supported.</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">System for Cross-domain Identity Management (SCIM) Clients</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e194a90e3dbb75bea8cc62654c82ca6ad\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP is compliant with certain parts of SCIM 2.0 specs marked by MUST and the related terms. All the software, services that are compliant with the same parts are supported. The already considered and supported vendors according to these directives are these:</span>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e8ea0bf7be6a7d917fdea69949c05d2fc\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Microsoft Entra</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"ea8536fe8ee828ce4a2c3c3154d5d462c\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Okta</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e014ccbf0b63d9aeb81e048437bc0ac11\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CyberArk Identity</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e72c09138bcf355d045f04db20d425818\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ping Identity (UnboundID)</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-font-size-medium\" data-list-item-id=\"e3ec45b43b96e397b0f9ffb03e4aa9802\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OneLogin</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBVEHX7JRD4YPEW11WDM7Y69\"><a href=\"#notes\" id=\"notes\">Notes</a></h2>\n\n<p>Liferay DXP does not restrict the use of VM/Container strategy as long as the Application Server, Database, JDK, Operating System, and Integrated Technology are certified for use as indicated on the Compatibility Matrix above. Subscribers will be responsible for configuring the VM/Container appropriately.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-small\">Updated 4/7/26</span></p>"
      },
